{
  "texts": [
    "proposed a novel multimodal method called TripletMultiDTI that leverages triplet loss and task prediction loss to accomplish this goal.",
    "This method provides a new framework that fuses the multimodal knowledge to predict interaction affinity labels.",
    "TripletMultiDTI also offers a novel loss function based on the triplet loss to learn more discriminative depiction.",
    "Using this model, researchers improved prediction results, as evident from the proposed approach's evaluation on three putative datasets (Dehghan et al., 2023).",
    "Palhamkhani et al."
